      static class  MMCal.Squeeze
      This Class implements methods to reduce dimension of the input data The reduction can concern different ways and is equivalent to the matlab squeeze function Squeeze sq = new MMCal.Squeeze(); sq.cal(m); double inter = (double) sq.getSqueeze().get(0); or double[] inter = (double[]) sq.getSqueeze().get(0); or double[][] inter = (double[][]) sq.getSqueeze().get(0); or double[][][] inter = (double[][][]) sq.getSqueeze().get(0); Copyright: Copyright (c) 2016 Company: Labex Archimède AMU Aix Marseille Université
